Novice Panel Missions

■Raise an ally's crystal STR LV to 90
Strategy Tip:
• Crystal materials up to high clusters can be obtained from cycle quests.
• Mighty shards can be obtained as rewards from event missions.
　*The crystals needed to clear this mission can be obtained by clearing the mission "Clear Act 1, Ch. 1, 'Primus Island.'"
• Refer to the game guide pages below for more information on crystal strength.
